<item>
 <title>Timeline of Symfony in Drupal 8 related issues and posts</title>
 <link>http://peterlozano.com/symfony-drupal-8-related-issues-posts</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;In preparation for &lt;a href=&quot;http://2012.drupalcamp.es/es/sesiones/symfony-en-drupal-8-los-detalles-101&quot;&gt;my talk at Drupalcamp Spain 2012 about Symfony in Drupal 8&lt;/a&gt; I made a list of some relevant issues and posts related to the topic. In pretty much chronological order.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;TIMELINE&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

