&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Conclusion&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;inline inline-none&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://peterlozano.com/sites/peterlozano.com/files/imagecache/preview/ifa_upload/img_5690.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; title=&quot;Barcelona view&quot;   /&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;caption&quot; style=&quot;width: -2px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Barcelona view&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	All of the above plus the official parties, the crowded Barcelona streets, the spanish summer weather and the many mojitos made this a very nice and productive event that I&#039;ll be looking forward to attend more in the future and we recommend you to do so.&lt;/p&gt;
